| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3572 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 682f8b3a-9cc8-5c27-8752-c6c08b27defc"
